Jeff Stanzler is an American screenwriter and director.He wrote and directed the 2005 psychological thriller, Sorry, Haters, an &quot;official selection&quot; in both the Toronto and American Film Institute film festivals.He is currently working on a documentary about politics in West Africa.He's married to Annouchka Yameogo-Stanzler.

Selected filmography
*''Sorry, Haters'' (2005)

